query:
INSERT INTO plt_tokens (
                index,
                token_id,
                transaction_index,
                name,
                decimal,
                issuer_index,
                issuer,
                module_reference,
                metadata,
                initial_supply
            ) VALUES (
                (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(index) + 1, 0) FROM plt_tokens),
                $1,
                $2,
                $3,
                $4,
                (SELECT index FROM accounts WHERE address = $5),
                $6,
                $7,
                $8,
                $9
                              )
